# ============================================================================
# Voter PII — NEVER commit. Raw voter files and any minimized index artifacts
# built from them stay on the operator's machine only; only scoped, minimized
# artifacts move to devices over the authenticated sync channel. Misuse of voter
# data is criminal in many states — this guard is load-bearing, not cosmetic.
# ============================================================================
